OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FToday felt like a moment.
OL,8,FOstensibly it was just a camera in a
OL,9,Fcourtroom but in reality this was a
OL,10,Fstep towards a more transparent
OL,11,Fjudicial system, a move towards
OL,12,Fhelping the public understand the role
OL,13,Fof judges and how they get to often
OL,14,Fdifficult and sensitive decisions.JThe
OL,15,Fjourney to stepping into that
OL,16,Fcourtroom with our cameraman John
OL,17,FVennard has been a long one, decades
OL,18,Fin the making.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/9
