OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FIt started with an innovative report
OL,7,Ffrom the Bar Council in 1989 which
OL,8,Frecommended televising court
OL,9,Fproceedings but it took 15 years to
OL,10,Factually happen when a pilot
OL,11,Finitiative to film at the Court of
OL,12,FAppeal in London took place.
OL,14,FMany characters worked behind the
OL,15,Fscenes to make this happen including
OL,16,Fthe legendary ITN Legal Counsul, John
OL,17,FBattle who worked tirelessly to bridge
OL,18,Fthe gap between the legal and
OL,19,Fbroadcast worlds.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/9
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
