OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FIt would still take another few years
OL,7,Fbefore regular filming started to take
OL,8,Fplace at the Supreme Court but those
OL,9,Fefforts have resulted in the most
OL,10,Fimportant rulings of our times being
OL,11,Ftelevised and watched by millions.
OL,12,FThink of the judgments handed down to
OL,13,FLucy Letby or the murderer of Sarah
OL,14,FEverard, former policeman Wayne
OL,15,FCouzens.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/9
