OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FThe Lady Chief Justice Siobhan Keegan
OL,7,Fhas vocalised her desire for reform
OL,8,Fand to make the workings of the courts
OL,9,Fmore accessible to the public and when
OL,10,Fat a dinner in London, she met John
OL,11,FBattle and the rest as they say is
OL,12,Fhistory.JJohn has been working with my
OL,13,Fteam at UTV but also with the BBC, PA
OL,14,Fand Sky News to get the Northern
OL,15,FIreland pilot off the ground.
OL,17,FIt's fair to say there are more
OL,18,Fsensitivities around the move than
OL,19,Fthere may be in other parts of the UK,
OL,20,Fanother legacy of the Troubles.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/9
