OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FBut all of us recognise that this is a
OL,7,Fmove which is in the public interest
OL,8,Fand while hugely sensitive, this is a
OL,9,Fprocess which could deliver
OL,10,Fsignificant reform and visibility to
OL,11,Fthe courts system.
OL,13,FOn a personal level, I think it
OL,14,Fhumanises what is often an opaque
OL,15,Fprocess. Rather than reading about a
OL,16,Fguilty or not guilty verdict or an
OL,17,Fappeal decision, it allows the public
OL,18,Fto understand the rationale behind the
OL,19,Fjudge's decision.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/9
