OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FIt helps them to understand the
OL,7,Fvarious nuances, often distressing
OL,8,Fissues which need to be considered and
OL,9,Fthe legal framework which judges have
OL,10,Fto work within.JAnd so to today.
OL,12,FJust being in the court with a camera
OL,13,Ffor the very first time felt
OL,14,Fauspicious.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/9
