OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FIt garnered interest from public,
OL,7,Fstaff and legal teams alike. While
OL,8,Fmyself and John concentrated on
OL,9,Fensuring everything worked from a
OL,10,Ftechnical perspective, we also
OL,11,Fappreciated that we were the face of
OL,12,Fthis pilot. We needed to ensure people
OL,13,Ffelt comfortable with the idea of a
OL,14,Fcamera in court.
OL,16,FWatch: Solicitor Paul Dougan reacts to
OL,17,Fnews of the pilot project.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/9
