OL,3,CCamera in the courtroom a long time
OL,4,Ccoming
OL,6,FOur level of professionalism would
OL,7,Finstil confidence in the process and
OL,8,Fas we stood there, it felt as if we
OL,9,Fcould be on the cusp of a new era of
OL,10,Ftransparency and visibility of those
OL,11,Fon the bench.JIt's day one however.
OL,12,FThere will be other test cases and
OL,13,Flegislative changes will have to be
OL,14,Fmade if putting cameras in our courts
OL,15,Fis to become as normal as it is in
OL,16,Fother parts of the UK. But today marks
OL,17,Fthe first step in what could be an
OL,18,Fexciting era for both the media and
OL,19,Fthe public.
